    "updated_at": "2015-10-26T02:01:19Z",
    "body": "Ok, closing my own issue and putting this as reference:\n\nFrom the renderer process (remote webpage), instead of `__dirname`, use [`app.getAppPath()`](http://electron.atom.io/docs/latest/api/app/#app-getapppath).\n\n``` coffeescript\nremote = require 'remote'\napp = remote.require('app')\nconsole.log app.getAppPath()\n```\n"
